original_sql: SELECT MAX(p.p_size) AS max_p_p_size, MIN(p.p_size) AS min_p_p_size, s.s_comment AS s_s_comment, MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment, MAX(p.p_partkey) AS max_p_p_partkey FROM part p, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT MAX(p_size) FROM (SELECT p_size, p_type FROM part JOIN lineitem ON p_partkey = l_partkey WHERE p_retailprice > 100 ) AS t_1 GROUP BY p_type ORDER BY p_type) AND EXISTS (SELECT SUM(l_extendedprice) FROM (SELECT l_extendedprice, l_returnflag FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey ) AS t_2 GROUP BY l_returnflag ORDER BY l_returnflag) AND s.s_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM (SELECT l_linenumber FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 20 UNION ALL SELECT o_shippriority FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500) t JOIN part ON p_partkey = t.l_linenumber) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_type FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE p_size > 10 ) AS t_4 GROUP BY p_type ORDER BY p_type) AND p.p_mfgr IN (SELECT p_mfgr FROM (SELECT p_mfgr, p_size FROM part WHERE p_size = 10 ) AS subq_5 WHERE p_size > 9 ORDER BY p_size) AND p.p_size = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer JOIN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01') AS subq_6 ON customer.c_custkey = subq_6.o_custkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION SELECT DISTINCT r_name FROM region WHERE r_regionkey = 1 UNION SELECT DISTINCT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_size > 12) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_mfgr FROM (SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1997-06-30' UNION SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount < 0.05) UNION ALL SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_returnflag = 'Y' UNION ALL SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_linestatus = 'F')) t GROUP BY p_mfgr) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_totalprice FROM (SELECT o_totalprice, o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_custkey = 10 ) AS subq_9 WHERE o_custkey > 9 ORDER BY o_custkey) AND p.p_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey, p_name FROM part WHERE p_size > 20 ) t) AND p.p_container LIKE 'JUMBO JAR%' AND p.p_partkey = 139907 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000001518%' AND s.s_nationkey <= 23 AND s.s_acctbal <= 2445.866520615661 AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#4%' AND s.s_suppkey < 2612 AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#31%' AND p.p_name LIKE 'linen lemon dodger almond gainsboro%' AND p.p_retailprice < 1385.663043043243  GROUP BY SELECT l.l_extendedprice AS l_l_extendedprice, c.c_comment AS c_c_comment, SUM(c.c_nationkey) AS sum_c_c_nationkey, AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_p_p_retailprice, MIN(l.l_extendedprice) AS min_l_l_extendedprice FROM customer c, lineitem l, part p WHERE p.p_container IN (SELECT p_container FROM (SELECT p_container, p_retailprice FROM part WHERE p_retailprice = 20 ) AS subq_1 WHERE p_retailprice > 15 ORDER BY p_retailprice) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_phone FROM (SELECT c_phone FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate BETWEEN '1996-01-01' AND '1996-12-31' UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000) UNION ALL SELECT c_phone FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '2-HIGH' UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'O')) t GROUP BY c_phone) AND l.l_linestatus IN (SELECT l_linestatus FROM (SELECT l_linestatus, l_extendedprice FROM lineitem ) AS subq_3 UNION SELECT r_comment FROM region) AND EXISTS (SELECT MIN(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE ps_availqty > 100 UNION SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN lineitem ON p_partkey = l_partkey WHERE l_quantity > 30 AND l_shipmode IN (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate < '1995-01-01')) AS subq_4 GROUP BY p_brand) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' UNION SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity < 10 AND l_shipdate IN (SELECT l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1997-01-01')) AS subq_5 GROUP BY o_orderpriority) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 150 ) UNION SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 150 ) ORDER BY p_brand) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_name FROM customer UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation UNION SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT n_name FROM nation AS n1_7 WHERE n_regionkey = 1) AS subq_7) AND l.l_discount = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 8000 UNION ALL SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 50) t JOIN customer ON c_custkey = t.s_suppkey) AND c.c_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_size > 10 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 50) t JOIN supplier ON s_suppkey = t.p_partkey) AND p.p_container IN (SELECT p_container FROM (SELECT p_container, p_size FROM part ) AS subq_10 UNION SELECT s_address FROM supplier) AND c.c_nationkey < 9 AND p.p_partkey <= 88022 AND c.c_custkey > 98382 AND l.l_shipdate > '1992-01-13' AND l.l_orderkey = 4053241 AND l.l_receiptdate > '1993-11-01' AND p.p_container LIKE 'MED PACK%' AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000004156%' AND p.p_size <= 10 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'AUTOMOBILE%'  GROUP BY c.c_comment, l.l_extendedprice LIMIT 10;

SELECT MIN(s.s_address) AS min_s_s_address, MAX(l.l_shipinstruct) AS max_l_l_shipinstruct, MIN(s.s_name) AS min_s_s_name, l.l_discount AS l_l_discount, MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment FROM lineitem l, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT o_1.o_clerk FROM orders o_1 WHERE o_1.o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_1.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l_1 WHERE l_1.l_discount > 0.05 UNION ALL SELECT l2_1.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l2_1 WHERE l2_1.l_shipdate < DATE '1995-06-01' GROUP BY l2_1.l_orderkey) AND o_1.o_totalprice < 5000) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(s_suppkey) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey, s_nationkey FROM supplier JOIN nation ON s_nationkey = n_nationkey WHERE s_acctbal < 5000 ) AS t_2 GROUP BY s_nationkey ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM (SELECT o_custkey, COUNT(*) FROM orders GROUP BY o_custkey HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AS subq_3) AS t_3) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_mfgr FROM (SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 30 ) UNION ALL SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_retailprice < 50) t GROUP BY p_mfgr ORDER BY p_mfgr) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey ) AS t_5 GROUP BY p_brand ORDER BY p_brand) AND l.l_quantity = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_size > 10 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 50) t JOIN supplier ON s_suppkey = t.p_partkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_7.p_brand FROM part p_7 WHERE p_7.p_partkey IN (SELECT l_7.l_partkey FROM lineitem l_7 WHERE l_7.l_discount > 0.1 UNION ALL SELECT l2_7.l_partkey FROM lineitem l2_7 WHERE l2_7.l_shipdate > DATE '1995-12-31' GROUP BY l2_7.l_partkey) AND p_7.p_size > 15) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_8.o_orderstatus FROM orders o_8 WHERE o_8.o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_8.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l_8 WHERE l_8.l_quantity < 15 UNION ALL SELECT l2_8.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l2_8 WHERE l2_8.l_extendedprice > 800 GROUP BY l2_8.l_orderkey) AND o_8.o_totalprice > 3000) AND EXISTS (SELECT s_acctbal FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 60 ) UNION SELECT s_acctbal FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 60 ) ORDER BY s_acctbal) AND s.s_phone IN (SELECT s_phone FROM (SELECT s_phone, s_nationkey FROM supplier ) AS subq_10 UNION SELECT p_brand FROM part) AND s.s_suppkey = 9309 AND l.l_tax >= 0.07471063260877911 AND l.l_shipinstruct LIKE 'COLLECT COD%' AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'F%' AND l.l_discount >= 0.03898142584816681 AND l.l_extendedprice <= 33171.50790992439 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'FOB%' AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'R%' AND l.l_quantity = 32.630118179574296 AND s.s_acctbal > -339.48232650733826  GROUP BY l.l_discount LIMIT 50;

SELECT MIN(l.l_comment) AS min_l_l_comment, MIN(l.l_linenumber) AS min_l_l_linenumber, COUNT(l.l_shipmode) AS count_l_l_shipmode, SUM(l.l_linenumber) AS sum_l_l_linenumber, COUNT(c.c_phone) AS count_c_c_phone FROM customer c, lineitem l, nation n, supplier s WHERE n.n_name IN (SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT n_name, n_regionkey FROM nation ) AS subq_1 UNION SELECT p_container FROM part) AND l.l_orderkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_returnflag) FROM lineitem JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F') AS order_union_2 ON l_linenumber) FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.05 UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION ALL SELECT 0 FROM part WHERE p_type = 'STANDARD') AND EXISTS (SELECT l_shipmode FROM (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_orderkey IN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1994-01-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 25) t GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY l_shipmode) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier UNION SELECT l_suppkey FROM (SELECT l_suppkey, COUNT(*) FROM lineitem GROUP BY l_suppkey HAVING COUNT(*) > 10) AS subq_6) AS t_6) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(p_size) FROM (SELECT p_size, p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_retailprice > 50 ) t GROUP BY p_mfgr ORDER BY p_mfgr) AND WHERE o_totalprice > 5000) AS order_union_9 ON lineitem.l_orderkey = order_union_9.o_orderkey) AND s.s_acctbal > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_partkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_suppkey IN (SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 7000 UNION SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 2)) AND c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND s.s_suppkey > 2550 AND c.c_nationkey <= 22 AND l.l_orderkey = 3838389 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'TRUCK%' AND l.l_linenumber > 4 AND n.n_regionkey <= 1 AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'A%' AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000007387%' AND l.l_tax = 0.06923129711040864 AND l.l_discount >= 0.08368914078784752  LIMIT 10;

l_discount = 0.1) AND 1+1 = 2) AND EXISTS (SELECT s_4.s_name FROM supplier s_4 WHERE s_4.s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_4.ps_suppkey FROM partsupp ps_4 WHERE ps_4.ps_supplycost > 200 UNION ALL SELECT ps2_4.ps_suppkey FROM partsupp ps2_4 WHERE ps2_4.ps_availqty < 30 GROUP BY ps2_4.ps_suppkey) AND s_4.s_acctbal < 1000) AND o.o_orderkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 30) AND o.o_orderpriority IN (SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipmode = 'AIR' ) UNION SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipmode = 'TRUCK' ) ORDER BY o_orderpriority) AND o.o_orderkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_orderstatus FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity > 10 UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity > 20 UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity > 30)) AND n.n_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM (SELECT c_custkey, c_name FROM customer ) t) AND p.p_retailprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey, s_phone FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 3000 ) t) AND ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey AND n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = 4248 AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#3%' AND ps.ps_supplycost <= 274.8278107800141 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'F%' AND ps.ps_availqty >= 7549 AND o.o_orderdate > '1994-01-22' AND s.s_suppkey <= 8731 AND n.n_name LIKE 'MOZAMBIQUE%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#21%' AND s.s_nationkey > 21  LIMIT 100;

SELECT AVG(o.o_totalprice) AS avg_o_o_totalprice, AVG(ps.ps_availqty) AS avg_ps_ps_availqty, p.p_size AS p_p_size, AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_ps_ps_supplycost, MIN(o.o_comment) AS min_o_o_comment FROM orders o, part p, partsupp ps WHERE EXISTS (SELECT o_clerk FROM (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1995-06-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500) t GROUP BY o_clerk ORDER BY o_clerk) AND EXISTS (SELECT SUM(c_acctbal) FROM (SELECT c_acctbal, c_nationkey FROM customer JOIN nation ON c_nationkey = n_nationkey WHERE c_acctbal > 1000 ) AS t_2 GROUP BY c_nationkey ORDER BY c_nationkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(p_size) FROM (SELECT p_size, p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_retailprice > 50 ) t GROUP BY p_mfgr ORDER BY p_mfgr) AND o.o_totalprice > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_name FROM part UNION ALL SELECT r_comment FROM region ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT l_shipmode FROM (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_orderkey IN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1994-01-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 25) t GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY l_shipmode) AND p.p_size = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_suppkey) FROM (SELECT ps_suppkey, ps_availqty FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(c_acctbal) FROM (SELECT c_acctbal, c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey BETWEEN 10 AND 20 ) t GROUP BY c_mktsegment ORDER BY c_mktsegment) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_address FROM (SELECT c_address, c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' ) AS subq_8 WHERE c_mktsegment != 'BUILDING' ORDER BY c_mktsegment) AND ps.ps_suppkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_returnflag) FROM lineitem JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F') AS order_union_9 ON lineitem.l_orderkey = order_union_9.o_orderkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_10.o_orderpriority FROM orders o_10 WHERE o_10.o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_10.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l_10 WHERE l_10.l_shipmode = 'AIR' UNION ALL SELECT l2_10.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l2_10 WHERE l2_10.l_returnflag = 'N' GROUP BY l2_10.l_orderkey) AND o_10.o_totalprice > 2000) AND p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey AND p.p_name LIKE 'lace bisque drab plum maroon%' AND p.p_retailprice <= 1224.5277154687033 AND p.p_partkey < 126035 AND ps.ps_suppkey = 9662 AND ps.ps_supplycost = 626.4235159328151 AND o.o_totalprice > 459762.6842236397 AND p.p_container LIKE 'WRAP PACK%' AND p.p_size >= 19 AND o.o_orderdate >= '1997-07-01' AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'O%'  GROUP BY p.p_size LIMIT 10;

SELECT ps.ps_availqty AS ps_ps_availqty, c.c_name AS c_c_name, MIN(o.o_shippriority) AS min_o_o_shippriority, SUM(ps.ps_suppkey) AS sum_ps_ps_suppkey, AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_c_c_acctbal FROM customer supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 70 UNION SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 4000) AND s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation JOIN region ON n_regionkey = r_regionkey WHERE r_name = 'ASIA')) AND o.o_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey, p_retailprice FROM part WHERE p_container = 'SM BOX' ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_type FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE p_size > 10 ) AS t_4 GROUP BY p_type ORDER BY p_type) AND EXISTS (SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000 ) UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 5000 ) ORDER BY n_name) AND c.c_name IN (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' ) UNION SELECT c_name FROM customer partsupp ps_7 WHERE ps_7.ps_supplycost > 75 UNION ALL SELECT ps2_7.ps_partkey FROM partsupp ps2_7 WHERE ps2_7.ps_availqty < 50 GROUP BY ps2_7.ps_partkey) AND p_7.p_retailprice < 100) AND ps.ps_availqty > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer JOIN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01') AS subq_8 ON customer.c_custkey = subq_8.o_custkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT l_shipinstruct FROM (SELECT l_shipinstruct, l_discount FROM lineitem ) AS subq_9 UNION SELECT r_comment FROM region) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_size FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_tax > 0.03 ) UNION SELECT p_size FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_tax < 0.03 ) ORDER BY p_size) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND n.n_nationkey > 21 AND o.o_custkey > 68301 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'F%' AND ps.ps_partkey = 191484 AND ps.ps_suppkey <= 1478 AND o.o_orderdate <= '1997-11-04' AND c.c_acctbal <= 7307.97031610239 AND o.o_totalprice <= 11255.880858675057 AND ps.ps_availqty > 4305 AND c.c_custkey < 132456  GROUP BY c.c_name, ps.ps_availqty LIMIT 10;

SELECT MIN(l.l_tax) AS min_l_l_tax, l.l_comment AS l_l_comment, COUNT(l.l_shipmode) AS count_l_l_shipmode, MAX(l.l_linestatus) AS max_l_l_linestatus, MAX(l.l_returnflag) AS max_l_l_returnflag FROM FROM lineitem WHERE l_linestatus = 'F')) t GROUP BY p_mfgr) AND EXISTS (SELECT MIN(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE ps_availqty > 100 UNION SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN lineitem ON p_partkey = l_partkey WHERE l_quantity > 30 AND l_shipmode IN (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate < MAX(s_acctbal) FROM (SELECT s_acctbal, s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey BETWEEN 1 AND 5 ) t GROUP BY s_nationkey ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND l.l_discount = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_suppkey) FROM (SELECT ps_suppkey, ps_availqty FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10 ) t) AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'N%' AND n.n_name LIKE 'ARGENTINA%' AND l.l_partkey = 160742 AND n.n_nationkey > 7 AND n.n_regionkey <= 0 AND l.l_commitdate >= '1998-06-29' AND l.l_shipinstruct LIKE 'DELIVER IN PERSON%' AND l.l_quantity = 29.363819401563315 AND l.l_suppkey >= 9948 AND l.l_discount >= 0.0688047961014152  GROUP BY l.l_comment LIMIT 50;

SELECT o.o_shippriority AS o_o_shippriority, MAX(o.o_orderpriority) AS max_o_o_orderpriority, MAX(o.o_comment) AS max_o_o_comment, o.o_clerk AS o_o_clerk, SUM(l.l_quantity) AS sum_l_l_quantity FROM
